{"tid":201222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戰雲密佈】解放軍北部戰區緊急部署 陸海空火箭軍聯合作戰","createTime":"2017-04-14T14:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T15:45:48.000Z","uid":28366,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be2854cff159dcdccb635f0fe62bead99df0ee66","tid":201222,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T14:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/14/225953_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F14%2F225953_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=18be353e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據總部位於香港的中國人權民運信息中心透露，因應朝鮮半島局勢，今天200名北部戰區陸、海、空、火箭軍的將校軍官，已在瀋陽北部戰區「聯合作戰指揮中心」緊急集結，並已制定應對目前朝鮮半島危機的作戰計劃。<br />\n<br />\n該中心稱，解放軍以前的「瀋陽軍區」有詳細的應對北韓危機向作戰計劃，但北部軍區近日的作戰計劃可能有別於前瀋陽軍區，因為要進行區陸、海、空、火箭軍的「聯合作戰」。<br />\n<br />\n中國人權民運信息中心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170414&amp;guid=56566063&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170414%26guid%3D56566063%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c27814a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170414%26guid%3D56566063%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=35018683\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170414&amp;guid=56566063&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"1c0104f24c914d4ea2591c2fcacb71cf12f03809","tid":201222,"uid":7704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T15:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022c13b4525d7ac10ab6a3b9275dca7dbba50d60","tid":201222,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"<block